{"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"text":"@discardableResult","kind":"attribute"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"beginEnrollmentVerification","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"identity","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:SS","text":"String"},{"kind":"text","text":") -> "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.youreyeonly.yeofr.YEOFR\/documentation\/YEOFR\/FRSDKReturnCode","preciseIdentifier":"s:5YEOFR15FRSDKReturnCodeO","text":"FRSDKReturnCode"}],"platforms":["iOS","iPadOS","Mac Catalyst"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The walk also PATCHES the gaps it measures: an FRR moment (the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"gallery fails the live user) feeds the rejected-positive capture","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"pipeline — accumulate, vet (consistency 0.90), guard (anchor 0.70","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"walk-1 parity, cross-identity, novelty) — and the staged centroids","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"are appended to the in-memory gallery at finish, so the host’s","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"post-walk persist saves the patched gallery (","type":"text"},{"code":"centroidsAdded","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" \/","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"code":"galleryCount","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" on the outcome; ","type":"text"},{"code":"rescuedFrames","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" counts the frames a"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"patch covered live). The measured FRR is always scored against the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"original gallery — patches never inflate it. Cancel discards the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"patches.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Hosts should run this between gallery completion and persisting"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the tracker, surface the rate to the user, and persist regardless","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"of the result (recommend a re-enrol on a low unpatched rate rather","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"than failing the save — reject loops strand users).","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Returns ","type":"text"},{"code":".trackerIsNull","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" when the identity isn’t enrolled or","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"another session owns the embedding feed (also the constant return","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"for engines without the verification walk, e.g. Luxand)."}]}]}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/yeofr\/yeofrsdk\/beginenrollmentverification(identity:)"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"sections":[],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/com.youreyeonly.yeofr.YEOFR\/documentation\/YEOFR\/YEOFRSDK\/beginEnrollmentVerification(identity:)"},"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.youreyeonly.yeofr.YEOFR\/documentation\/YEOFR","doc:\/\/com.youreyeonly.yeofr.YEOFR\/documentation\/YEOFR\/YEOFRSDK"]]},"metadata":{"title":"beginEnrollmentVerification(identity:)","fragments":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"beginEnrollmentVerification","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"identity","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"String","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:SS"},{"text":") -> ","kind":"text"},{"text":"FRSDKReturnCode","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:5YEOFR15FRSDKReturnCodeO"}],"symbolKind":"method","ro